    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK410">
<l>vilaṅkoṭu makka ḷaṉaiya rilaṅkunūl</l>
<l>kaṟṟārō ṭēṉai yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As beasts by the side of men, so are other men by the side of those who are learned in celebrated works.</l>
